# id: LobCreator -> void close()_
commentText:
Close this LobCreator session and free its temporarily created BLOBs and CLOBs._Will not need to do anything if using PreparedStatement's standard methods,_but might be necessary to free database resources if using proprietary means._

NOTE: Needs to be invoked after the involved PreparedStatements have_been executed or the affected O/R mapping sessions have been flushed._Otherwise, the database resources for the temporary BLOBs might stay allocated.
codeText: void close()_
